                | We already 24 hours fast services to help you. You can contact us at <a href="tel:8886175894">(888)617-5894</a>
          .about__photo
            img(src="../img/about/Image-works.png", alt="img-works")
    //- section services
    section.services#services
      .container
        .services__inner
          .services__titles
            h2 Our Services
            p.
              You have problems with leaking pipes, broken tiles, lost keys or want to tidy up the trees around you, of course you need our help!
          .services__our
            .services__col(data-aos="zoom-in")
              .services__col-icon
                img(src="../img/services/icon-1.svg", alt="icon")
              .services__col-text
                h3 Plumbing services
                p.
                  Drain pipe leaking, pipe clogged, replace the pipe line
            .services__col(data-aos="zoom-in")
              .services__col-icon
                img(src="../img/services/icon-2.svg", alt="icon")
              .services__col-text
                h3 Roofing repair
                p.
                  Roof leaks, tile replacement, roof cleaning and maintenance
            .services__col(data-aos="zoom-in")
              .services__col-icon
                img(src="../img/services/icon-3.svg", alt="icon")
              .services__col-text
                h3 Mold Removal
                p.
                  Removing and cleaning mildew, Restoration and Prevention
            .services__col(data-aos="zoom-in")
              .services__col-icon
                img(src="../img/services/icon-4.svg", alt="icon")
              .services__col-text
                h3 Tree Trimming
                p.
                  Trimming and cleaning, Deadwood removal, Tree shaping
            .services__col(data-aos="zoom-in")
              .services__col-icon
                img(src="../img/services/icon-5.svg", alt="icon")
              .services__col-text
                h3 Appliance Repair
                p.
                  repair of washing machines, refrigerators, Air conditioner, etc
            .services__col(data-aos="zoom-in")
              .services__col-icon
                img(src="../img/services/icon-6.svg", alt="icon")
              .services__col-text
                h3 Bathroom Remodeling
                p.
                  Design and Consulting, installation, Repairing, tile repair
            .services__col(data-aos="zoom-in")
              .services__col-icon
                img(src="../img/services/icon-7.svg", alt="icon")
              .services__col-text
                h3 Locksmith
                p.
                  Lock Installation and Repair, Duplication, Lock Rekeying
            .services__ask(data-aos="zoom-in")
              .services__ask-text
                div More service?
                p.
                  You can tell us what you need and we can help!
              .services__ask-btn
                a(href="#") Call Us Now
